long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Bring style to Chrome with Zero Two and BMW F36 live wallpapers, plus a search bar and quick-access icons for sleek browsing.


Combine anime flair with automotive luxury with the Zero Two and BMW F36 Live Wallpaper Chrome extension! Each new tab unveils a dynamic scene featuring Zero Two from Darling in the Franxx alongside the sleek, powerful BMW F36, blending the beauty of high-end cars with the charm of an iconic anime character. Perfect for fans of anime and car enthusiasts alike, these live wallpapers create a unique and stylish browsing experience.
The extension also includes a built-in Google search bar for efficient browsing and customizable quick-access icons for your favorite sites. This feature-rich design lets you enjoy both visual appeal and functionality, keeping everything you need just a click away.
Ideal for those who love anime and luxury cars, the Zero Two and BMW F36 Live Wallpaper extension adds a unique aesthetic to each new tab. Feel the cool blend of anime and automotive elegance with every click, bringing excitement and style to your online world!
